,(31,4,'izuchite-vliyaniye-gravitatsii-zemli-na-zaderzhku-radiosignalov-so-sputnikov','Изучите влияние гравитации Земли на задержку радиосигналов со спутников.','Yerning tortishish kuchi sun\'iy yo\'ldoshlardan kelgan radio signallarning kechikishiga ta\'sirini o\'rganing','Study the effects of Earth’s gravity on the time delay of radio signals from satellites',NULL,NULL,'<p>Организовал Мастер-класс ученых Астрономического института Улугбека на платформе Zoom для студентов университетов-партнеров.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/RayimbaevDR231020Erasmus.pdf\">Изучите эффекты&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/RayimbaevDR231020Erasmus.pdf\">Скачать в формате PDF</a></p>\r\n','<p>Hamkor universitetlar talabalari uchun Zoom platformasida Ulug&#39;bek Astronomiya Instituti olimlarining master-klassi tashkil etildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/RayimbaevDR231020Erasmus.pdf\">Ta&#39;sirlarni o&#39;rganing&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/RayimbaevDR231020Erasmus.pdf\">PDF formatida yuklab oling</a></p>\r\n','<p>Organized the Master-class of the scientists from Ulugh Bek Astronomical Institute in Zoom platform for the students of partner universities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Study the effects&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/RayimbaevDR231020Erasmus.pdf\">Download as PDF</a></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo_2020-12-11_22-40-44.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1628936955,NULL,1628936955,1630134393,NULL,0,1,1,1628936955,1628936955,1628936955,1628936955,0,0,0.0),(33,7,'onlayn-vstrecha-natsional-nykh-partnerov-proyekta','Онлайн-встреча национальных партнеров проекта','Loyihaning milliy sheriklarining onlayn uchrashuvi','Online meeting of the national partners of the project',NULL,NULL,'<p>Онлайн-встреча национальных партнеров проекта 27.04.2020<br />\r\nНа встрече обсуждались вопросы централизованной закупки оборудования, а именно утверждение перечня необходимого оборудования для учебных лабораторий, а также другие вопросы реализации проекта.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/2.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/3.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/4.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/5.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/6.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n','<p>Loyihaning milliy sheriklarining onlayn uchrashuvi 27/04/2020<br />\r\nUchrashuvda uskunalarni markazlashtirilgan holda sotib olish, ya&#39;ni o&#39;quv laboratoriyalari uchun zarur uskunalar ro&#39;yxatini tasdiqlash, shuningdek, loyihani amalga oshirishning boshqa masalalari muhokama qilindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/2.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/3.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/4.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/5.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/6.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online meeting of the national partners of the project 04/27/2020<br />\r\nAt the meeting, issues of centralized purchase of equipment were discussed, namely the approval of the list of necessary equipment for teaching laboratories, also other project implementation issues were discussed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/2.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/3.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/4.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/5.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/Online%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20partners%20of%20the%20project/6.png\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": null, \"meta_des_2\": null, \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": null, \"meta_keyword_2\": null, \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1628937367,NULL,1628937367,1630151438,NULL,0,1,1,1628937367,1628937367,1628937367,1628937367,0,0,0.0),(34,7,'pervyy-seminar-vstrecha-erasmus-v-ramkakh-proyekta-novaya-uchebnaya-programma-v-oblasti-kosmicheskikh-sistem-i-tekhniki-svyazi-spacecom-2','Первый семинар-встреча ERASMUS + в рамках проекта «Новая учебная программа в области космических систем и техники связи / SPACECOM».','ERASMUS + \"Kosmik tizimlar va kommunikatsiyalar muhandisligida yangi o\'rganish dasturi / SPACECOM\" loyihasining birinchi seminar-yig\'ilishi.','First ERASMUS + seminar-meeting of the project “New study program in space systems and communications engineering / SPACECOM”',NULL,NULL,'<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/1.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>3-5 марта 2020 года в Ташкентском университете информационных технологий (ТУИТ) состоится первый семинар-встреча в рамках проекта ERASMUS + &laquo;Новая учебная программа в области космических систем и техники связи / SPACECOM&raquo;.&nbsp;В мероприятии примут участие администрация ТУИТ, представители МВССО Узбекистана, участники проекта и заинтересованные стороны.&nbsp;В ходе мероприятия участники будут ознакомлены с целями и ожидаемыми результатами проекта&nbsp;<strong>SPACECOM</strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;Кроме того, в ходе мероприятия между участниками проекта будут обсуждаться вопросы совместной работы над проектом.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/2.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Участники проекта:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TUIT, Технический университет Берлина (Германия), Университет Сорбоны (Франция), Университет прикладных наук Artesis-Plantijn (Бельгия), Технический университет Софии (Болгария), EXOLAUNCH (Германия), Coursento (Германия), Каршинский филиал TUIT , Филиальный центр переподготовки и повышения квалификации педагогических кадров при ТУИТ, Ферганский политехнический институт, Туринский политехнический институт в Ташкенте, Ташкентский государственный технический университет, Национальный университет Узбекистана, Астрономический институт АН РУз.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Срок реализации проекта - три года: 2019-2022 гг.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/3.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/4.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Основные цели проекта:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Развитие и модернизация существующей магистерской программы в области спутниковых технологий, космических технологий и систем связи, а также использование спутниковой связи в соответствии с рекомендациями Болонского процесса.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Основные ожидаемые результаты проекта:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- открыта новая магистерская программа по космической технике и технологиям;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- модернизация существующих и разработка новых курсов, связанных с космической и коммуникационной инженерией;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- организация новой учебно-научно-исследовательской лаборатории космической техники и технологий;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- переподготовка кадров ТУИТ и его филиалов;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- разработка новых справочников и учебно-методических пособий.</p>\r\n','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/1.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2020 yil 3-5 mart kunlari Toshkent axborot texnologiyalari universitetida (TATU) ERASMUS + loyihasi doirasida &quot;Kosmik tizimlar va aloqa muhandisligida yangi o&#39;rganish dasturi / SPACECOM&quot; birinchi seminar-yig&#39;ilishi bo&#39;lib o&#39;tadi.&nbsp;Tadbirda TATU ma&#39;muriyati, O&#39;zbekiston Sog&#39;liqni saqlash vazirligi vakillari, loyiha ishtirokchilari va loyihaning manfaatdor tomonlari ishtirok etadi.&nbsp;Tadbir davomida ishtirokchilar&nbsp;<strong>SPACECOM</strong>&nbsp;loyihasining&nbsp;maqsadlari va kutilgan natijalari bilan&nbsp;<strong>tanishadilar</strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;Bundan tashqari, tadbir davomida loyiha ishtirokchilari o&#39;rtasida loyihada jamoaviy ishlash bo&#39;yicha munozaralar bo&#39;lib o&#39;tadi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/2.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Loyiha ishtirokchilari:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TATU, Berlin Texnik Universiteti (Germaniya), Sorbona Universiteti (Frantsiya), Artesis-Plantijn Amaliy Fanlar Universiteti (Belgiya), Sofiya Texnik Universiteti (Bolgariya), EXOLAUNCH (Germaniya), Coursento (Germaniya), TATU Qarshi filiali , TATU qoshidagi pedagog kadrlarni qayta tayyorlash va malakasini oshirish filiali markazi, Farg&#39;ona politexnika instituti, Toshkentdagi Turin politexnika instituti, Toshkent davlat texnika universiteti, O&#39;zbekiston Milliy universiteti, O&#39;zbekiston Fanlar akademiyasi Astronomiya instituti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loyiha muddati uch yil: 2019-2022 yillar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/3.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/4.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Loyihaning asosiy maqsadlari:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sun&#39;iy yo&#39;ldosh texnologiyasi, kosmik texnologiyalar va aloqa tizimlari bo&#39;yicha mavjud magistrlik dasturini ishlab chiqish va modernizatsiya qilish, shuningdek, Boloniya jarayonining tavsiyalariga muvofiq sun&#39;iy yo&#39;ldosh aloqasidan foydalanish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Loyihaning kutilayotgan asosiy natijalari:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- kosmik injeneriya va texnologiya bo&#39;yicha yangi magistrlik dasturi ochildi;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- mavjudni modernizatsiya qilish va kosmik va kommunikatsiya injeneriyasi bilan bog&#39;liq yangi kurslarni ishlab chiqish;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-kosmik injeneriya va texnologiya bo&#39;yicha yangi o&#39;quv-ilmiy tadqiqot laboratoriyasini tashkil etish;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-TATU va uning filiallarini qayta tayyorlash;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-yangi qo&#39;llanma va o&#39;quv-uslubiy qo&#39;llanmalar ishlab chiqish.</p>\r\n','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/1.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On March 3-5 of 2020 at the Tashkent University of Information Technology (TUIT) will be held first seminar-meeting within the framework of ERASMUS + project &ldquo;New study program in space systems and communications engineering / SPACECOM&rdquo;. The event will be attended the TUIT administration, representatives of the MHSSE of Uzbekistan, project participants and project stakeholders. During the event, participants will be acquainted with the goals and expected results of the&nbsp;<strong>SPACECOM</strong>&nbsp;project. In addition, during the event will be discussions between the project participants on teamwork for the project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/2.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Project participants:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TUIT, Technical University of Berlin (Germany), University of Sorbona (France), Artesis-Plantijn University of Applied Sciences (Belgium), Technical University of Sofia (Bulgaria), EXOLAUNCH (Germany), Coursento (Germany), Karshi branch of TUIT, Branch center of retraining and professional development of pedagogical staff under TUIT, Ferghana Polytechnic Institute, Turin Polytechnic Institute in Tashkent, Tashkent State Technical University, National University of Uzbekistan, Astronomical Institute of the Uzbek Academy of Sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The project period is three years: 2019-2022.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/3.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://st.spacecom.uz//elfinder-files/First%20ERASMUS%20%2B%20seminar-meeting/4.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The main objectives of the project are:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Development and modernization of the existing master&rsquo;s program in satellite technology, space technology and communication systems, as well as the use of satellite communications in accordance with the recommendations of the Bologna process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Expected Project Results:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; opening new master program in space engineering and technology has been opened;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; modernization of the existing and development of new courses related to Space and Communication Engineering;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; organizing new educational-scientific research laboratory for space engineering and technology;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; re-training personal of TUIT and its branches;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; developing new handbook and educational-methodological manuals.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": null, \"meta_des_2\": null, \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": null, \"meta_keyword_2\": null, \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1628937407,NULL,1628937407,1630129101,NULL,0,1,1,1