ontent/uploads/2020/12/Spacecom-Plus-Agreement.pdf\">Spacecom Plus shartnomasi&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Spacecom-Plus-Agreement.pdf\">PDF formatida yuklab olish</a></p>\r\n','<ul>\r\n	<li>Are you interested in getting access to the project materials?</li>\r\n	<li>Do you want to participate in the project-related events?</li>\r\n	<li>Are you looking for employee training?</li>\r\n	<li>Do you want to announce an internship to our students?</li>\r\n	<li>Are you hiring young specialists for the space and satellite industry?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>You are welcome to become part of the extended SPACECOM + network of educational, research and business institutions. We are looking forward to future cooperation!</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>Please fill in the questionnaire form and out ream will get in touch with you to sign the agreement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Spacecom-Plus-Agreement.pdf\">Spacecom Plus Agreement</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://spacecom.uz/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Spacecom-Plus-Agreement.pdf\">Download as PDF</a></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1630136452,NULL,1630136452,1630136452,NULL,0,1,1,1630136452,1630136452,1630136452,1630136452,0,0,0.0),(118,10,'tashkent-skiy-universitet-informatsionnykh-tekhnologiy-imeni-mukhammada-al-khorezmi-uzbekistan','Ташкентский университет информационных технологий имени Мухаммада аль-Х